---
title: Middle Eastern Salmon & Chickpea Bowls with Spiced Basmati Rice & Garlicky White Sauce
description: We swoon for shawarma. For this veggie-centric spin, we swap the traditional spit-roasted meat for roasted chickpeas, onion, and tomatoes, but keep all the same aromatic, warming spices. It’s all served over ultra-flavorful, spiced basmati rice. If you’re anything like us, one of our favorite parts about shawarma is the sauce selection—and don’t worry, we didn’t skimp. Drizzle hot sauce and a creamy, garlicky white sauce over the top, then prepare to be totally bowled over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61c233249f459f195a67fcf9-efdb0622.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/middle-eastern-salmon-chickpea-bowls-61c233249f459f195a67fcf9-2bb642be.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/middle-eastern-salmon-chickpea-bowls-61c233249f459f195a67fcf9
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Middle East
nutrition:
  calories: 980 kcal
  fat: 45 g
  saturated fat: 11 g
  carbohydrates: 97 g
